<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Nouveau message de contact</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: #4a4a4a;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #faf7f5;
        }
        .container {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 16px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #C07459 0%, #e8a090 50%, #7A9A8B 100%);
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            color: white;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
        }
        .header .logo {
            font-family: 'Brush Script MT', cursive;
            font-size: 32px;
            color: white;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        .info-box {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-left: 4px solid #C07459;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        .info-row {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .info-label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #C07459;
            font-size: 14px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        .message-box {
            background: white;
            border: 1px solid #eee;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            white-space: pre-wrap;
            color: #333;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 25px 30px;
            color: #888;
            font-size: 13px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">✨ {{ appName }}</div>
            <h1>Nouveau Message</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Bonjour,</p>
            <p>Vous avez reçu un nouveau message via le formulaire de contact du site.</p>

            <div class="info-box">
                <div class="info-row">
                    <div class="info-label">De</div>
                    <div>{{ name }} (<a href="mailto:{{ email }}" style="color: #C07459;">{{ email }}</a>)</div>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <div class="info-label">Sujet</div>
                    <div>{{ subject }}</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="info-label" style="margin-bottom: 10px;">Message :</div>
            <div class="message-box">{{ message }}</div>

            <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;">
                <a href="mailto:{{ email }}?subject=Re: {{ subject }}" style="display: inline-block; background: #C07459; color: white; text-decoration: none; padding: 12px 25px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: bold;">Répondre</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Ce message a été envoyé depuis le formulaire de contact de {{ appName }}.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
